{"tid":464844,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"大板周游卡 一問","createTime":"2017-11-11T02:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T15:54:27.000Z","uid":16869,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"716a9d7ddb0f79bd0c9518f2b7bcf4301834daa8","tid":464844,"uid":16869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T02:55:04.000Z","msg":"想問有無巴打買過大板周游卡<br />\n<br />\n大家建議買1定2日定無需要買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢有30幾樣設施<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.osaka-info.jp/osp/cht/facility/free\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.osaka-info.jp%2Fosp%2Fcht%2Ffacility%2Ffree&d=7VTm%2BqeeYZz6%2BOv%2BOZ%2BwxJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=203f4129\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.osaka-info.jp/osp/cht/facility/free</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/11/034812_08c4b75c4cd346f714df8654fc4cd7b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F11%2F034812_08c4b75c4cd346f714df8654fc4cd7b6.jpg&h=d2ab7e58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 去大板5日"},{"pid":"efc1adfeb5e8440fc9110c1f4db900e674ea8b2d","tid":464844,"uid":34692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T02:56:51.000Z","msg":"諗下自己想去邊<br />\n再計下個價錢，包括景點入場同車費<br />\n就知道買抵啲定唔買抵啲"},{"pid":"f7d2d00ece6bd1cdf4216f9c9793656175675bd4","tid":464844,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:00:57.000Z","msg":"2日 <br />\n利申 用過"},{"pid":"15cd92e014f4a353c930c2b0f110a26f425f4212","tid":464844,"uid":2247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:01:15.000Z","msg":"我買兩日"},{"pid":"1e01529b8e2881176f836b39bd8ce3c19e395666","tid":464844,"uid":57743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:04:00.000Z","msg":"你第二日會唔會坐地鐵<br />\n會就買2日<br />\n行到攰,又可以坐下摩天輪同船<br />\n好抵玩"},{"pid":"473a621dddcf2a33b6bca0579fa50d7412cf6592","tid":464844,"uid":21979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:08:03.000Z","msg":"2個摩天輪都抵番晒"},{"pid":"f34b179c5026e9edc87e7a31904be4a2f75fef02","tid":464844,"uid":41010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:16:53.000Z","msg":"注意返2日券心比1日可以搭嘅車好似係少左，要睇返點搭車<br />\n不過無論1定2日，你會去得多過3個入面有嘅景點，其實已經抵返"},{"pid":"2686f79cb07fe2991173312d799e4c3b0b4d58b9","tid":464844,"uid":41010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:17:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>注意返2日券比1日可以免費搭嘅車好似係少左，要睇返點搭車<br />\n不過無論1定2日，你會去得多過3個入面有嘅景點，其實已經抵返</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4ec612f94a03736cc0817437e8205eb2bac21275","tid":464844,"uid":16869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:22:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2個摩天輪都抵番晒</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望啲行程時間就到晒"},{"pid":"7513197395f3d43f456e6e6a9733da95bc57a5c6","tid":464844,"uid":33424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:23:20.000Z","msg":"你第一次去大阪就買2日<br />\n不過我去果陣只去過5個景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ca4a5f65e98dcc2863a59a6ba17cdbe87bf0b4","tid":464844,"uid":31108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:26:18.000Z","msg":"每次買一定去免費浴場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03bc263afaef9c440fd00f3729fd53c9d584c843","tid":464844,"uid":16869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T03:27:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你第一次去大阪就買2日<br />\n不過我去果陣只去過5個景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該會去埋京都,奈良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果買一日 睇嚟啲行程都要就返晒嗰啲所有景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0518cf4be5409fd196f2ac4076be1d4d08e044","tid":464844,"uid":56